"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/kmouth"
"\">help:/kmouth</ulink> (either enter this &URL; into &konqueror;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kmouth</"
"parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Existe documentación más detallada disponible en <ulink url=\"help:/kmouth"
"\">help:/kmouth</ulink> (introduzca este &URL; en &konqueror;, o ejecute "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kmouth</"
"parameter></userinput>)."

